Module scenebuilder.content.editor
Package com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.contenteditor.controller

Class ContentPanelController

java.lang.Object
com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.core.ui.AbstractPanelController
com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.core.ui.AbstractFxmlPanelController
com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.contenteditor.controller.ContentPanelController
All Implemented Interfaces:
Content, FxmlController, FXOMDocument.SceneGraphHolder
@Component
@Scope("document")
@Lazy
public class ContentPanelController
extends AbstractFxmlPanelController
implements Content, FXOMDocument.SceneGraphHolder
This class creates and controls the Content Panel of Scene Builder Kit.
